[ Fancy Tricks  with simple numbers ]
1. Min-Max Scaling
squeezes ( or stretches ) all feaure values to be within the range of [0,1].

# 1. 결측치 처리하기 ####
df <- data.frame( sex = c("M","F",NA, "M", "F"),
            score = c(5, 4,3,4,NA))
df
is.na(df)
table(is.na(df))
table(is.na(df$sex))
table(is.na(df$score))
